  <body>
<div class="container text-center">
    <h1 style="font-size:5vw">What is <span style ="color:#500000"> AIC </span> ACCESS?</h1>
        <p>AIC Access is an exclusive program for high-caliber, highly dedicated student who desire to complete a high
        -finance internship after their freshman, sophomore, or junior year. We partner with investment banks, private
        equity firms, and asset managers to provide opportunities for professional growth through a summer internship that may be
        an enigma to obtain.</p>
    </div>
<div class ="container p-3 my-3">
    <h3 style="font-size:40px"> Requirements </h3>
        <p> - Currently enroller as a full-time freshman,sophomore, or junior undergraduate student OR at least 1 summer 
        away from graduation </p> 
        <p> - Have a good academic background </p> 
        <p> - Preparation and devotion to career in finance-related feilds (Does not include corporate finance, wealth management, 
        or consulting) </p> 
</div>

<div class = "container p-3 my-3">
    <h3 style="font-size:40px"> How To Join </h3>
    <ol>
        <li> Build/Revise your resume to the template given in the appication </li><br>
        <li> Aply by clicking the button below </li><br>
        <li> Be on the lookout for an invitation to join AIC ACCESS to create a login </li><br>
        <li> Set up your log-in credentials and fill out all fields for your profile information (This may be shared with companies) </li>
    </ol>
</div>
<div class = "container text-center">
 <%= link_to '<button type="button" class ="btn btn-primary btn-block "> Apply Today </button>'.html_safe,new_access_submission_path %>
</div>

